{{ja-kanjitab|たもと|yomi=k}}
From {{inh|ja|ojp|sort=たもと|-}}, first attested in the ''{{w|Man'yōshū}}'' (''c.'' 759 {{CE}}).

Originally a compound of {{m|ja|手|tr=ta|pos=ancient combining form of ''te'', "[[arm]], [[hand]]"}} + {{m|ja|本|tr=moto||[[origin]]}}.<ref name="DJR"/><ref name="DJS">{{R:Daijisen}}</ref>

